15 WHEREAS, Congresswoman McBath has proudly represented metro Atlanta in Georgia's
16 Sixth Congressional District, working diligently to uplift and protect the communities she
17 serves through meaningful policy and action; and
18 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the outstanding accomplishments of this
19 remarkable and distinguished individual be appropriately honored.
20 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
21 the members of this body recognize and commend Congresswoman Lucy McBath for her
22 efficient, effective, unselfish, and dedicated public service as well as extend the most sincere
23 best wishes for continued health and happiness.
24 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
25 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to
26 Congresswoman Lucy McBath.
